# {{ project_name_title }} — Claude Code Context

## Stack

- Python 3.12, Poetry
- FastAPI backend
- jackknife for LLM, memory, and data tooling

## Commands

```bash
# Install
poetry install

# Run the API
poetry run uvicorn main:app --reload --port 8000

# Run tests
poetry run pytest

# Lint + format
poetry run ruff check . --fix
poetry run ruff format .
```

## API Endpoints

- `GET /health` — Health check
- `GET /` — Root

## Environment

Copy `.env.example` to `.env` and fill in secrets. Never commit `.env`.
